org.mini2Dx.ui.element

Class Column

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mini2Dx.ui.element.UiElement
      • org.mini2Dx.ui.element.Column
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Hoverable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Container, Row, ScrollBox

    public class Column
extends UiElement
    A column of UiElements. A column can be multiple columns wide with UiElements added horizontally and wrapping as required.
